 Director-General of NECA, Mr Timothy Olawale  In a statement, NECA expressed concern about the state of the Nigerian economy, calling on government to deepen engagement with the private sector as a way of fast-tracking job creation, investment generation and the development of the nation.
  
Director-General of NECA, Dr. Timothy Olawale, who called for urgent steps to salvage the economy, affirmed the commitment and readiness of organised businesses to continue to support government in the arduous task of nation building and economic renaissance.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .